{
  "texts": [
    "To further improve efficiency, another line of work drops [18,50,92] or compresses [3,70,73,102,112] tokens within LLMs.",
    "For example, PDrop [92] progressively prunes vision tokens across LLM layers.",
    "Although efficient, dropping tokens based on attention scores [5,121] can cause irreversible information loss.",
    "While token dropping is convenient and can be applied in a training-free manner, token compression avoids information loss.",
    "VoCo-LLaMA [102] and Video-XL [73] suggest compressing vision tokens into new special tokens."
  ]
}